title: Always Have a Plan B
itunes:title: Always Have a Plan B
description:
08/26/16 - On today's show rapper Vince Staples stops by and lets us know how he really feels about the industry and wanting to be successful. Next the show takes has an interesting discussion on something that has been successful for many women who don't want to be pregnant, which is the "Plan B" pill.
